Here's a bit of digging -- toy program that generates matmul

run_metadata = tf.RunMetadata()
a = tf.placeholder(dtype=np.float32)
b = tf.placeholder(dtype=np.float32)
c = tf.matmul(a, b)
sess = tf.InteractiveSession()
a0 = np.ones((3,3), dtype=np.float32)
feed_dict = {a: a0, b: a0}
sess.run([c], feed_dict=feed_dict,
         options=tf.RunOptions(trace_level=tf.RunOptions.FULL_TRACE),
         run_metadata=run_metadata)
print run_metadata.step_stats

...

timeline_label: "MatMul = MatMul(_recv_Placeholder_0, _recv_Placeholder_1_0)"

The result in shows no mention of inputs, that definition is in step_stats.proto so there are no inputs in proto but they are present in label

And it looks like timeline.py has _parse_op_label which extracts inputs from op label. So one thing to check would be to look at your run_metadata.step_stats and see what timeline_label is for the node in question and then check the label generating logic if it's missing inputs

body:
Here's a bit of digging -- toy program that generates matmul

```
run_metadata = tf.RunMetadata()
a = tf.placeholder(dtype=np.float32)
b = tf.placeholder(dtype=np.float32)
c = tf.matmul(a, b)
sess = tf.InteractiveSession()
a0 = np.ones((3,3), dtype=np.float32)
feed_dict = {a: a0, b: a0}
sess.run([c], feed_dict=feed_dict,
         options=tf.RunOptions(trace_level=tf.RunOptions.FULL_TRACE),
         run_metadata=run_metadata)
print run_metadata.step_stats

...

timeline_label: "MatMul = MatMul(_recv_Placeholder_0, _recv_Placeholder_1_0)"

```

The result in shows no mention of inputs, that definition is in [step_stats.proto](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/2a06837336bc29cb797c5be5605cb6188857768c/tensorflow/core/framework/step_stats.proto) so there are no inputs in proto but they are present in label

And it looks like `timeline.py` has `_parse_op_label` which extracts inputs from op label. So one thing to check would be to look at your `run_metadata.step_stats` and see what `timeline_label` is for the node in question and then check the label generating logic if it's missing inputs
